metadata.name: Wall Street Pepe
metadata.description: Wall Street Pepe ($WEPE) is a meme-based cryptocurrency inspired by internet culture, specifically targeting the "degen" crypto audience. It features a decentralized exchange (DEX) launch, meme-driven branding, and staking rewards. Designed to appeal to fans of meme coins and the "Pepe" character, the project emphasizes community and humor in its approach.
